=========================================
ONE-LINE FINAL SUMMARY
=========================================

STL containers are chosen based on tradeoff between ordering, speed, and memory:
- Tree (ordered, O(log n))
- Hash (fast, O(1))
- Array (vector/deque for cache efficiency)
- Linked list (pointer-based flexibility)
- Heap (priority_queue for top element access)

